ikh veys ⟨nit,⟩ shpeter hobn a- az es flegn, es zaynen arayngekumen shoyn fun Rusland,

00:11:36.785 --> 00:11:39.384
iz a groyser untershid gevezn

00:11:39.384 --> 00:11:43.194
tsvishn di yidn fun di rusn un di yidn fun letn,

00:11:43.260 --> 00:11:44.463
vi azoy?

00:11:43.412 --> 00:11:44.570
fun Letland.

00:11:44.463 --> 00:11:45.414
vi azoy?

00:11:48.930 --> 00:11:52.872
vayle zey hobn zikh gehodevet, mir hobn zikh gehodevet in,

00:11:52.896 --> 00:11:54.560
in erlekhkeyt.

00:11:55.275 --> 00:11:57.685
⟨undz hot men⟩ nit gedarft, mir hobn ⟨ge-⟩

00:11:57.685 --> 00:11:59.589
nit gedarft ganvenen.

00:11:59.798 --> 00:12:02.519
 der yingl,

00:12:02.519 --> 00:12:05.749
az er flegt tsugeyn un betn vos nit iz, flegt men im gebn.

00:12:06.042 --> 00:12:08.671
un di eltere mentshn flegn

00:12:08.671 --> 00:12:11.284
arbetn, un zey flegn gut arbetn;

00:12:13.045 --> 00:12:14.676
flegt men zey take,

00:12:15.525 --> 00:12:17.149
vi me zogt,

00:12:18.006 --> 00:12:19.265
batsoln.

00:12:20.115 --> 00:12:20.902
nu,

00:12:21.027 --> 00:12:23.884
groyse geltn flegt men nit tsoln, ober

00:12:23.884 --> 00:12:25.509
der mentsh flegt lebn.

00:12:26.410 --> 00:12:27.956
⟨er f-⟩ mentsh flegt lebn.

00:12:29.413 --> 00:12:32.495
un di vos zaynen gekumen fun, shpeter,

00:12:32.653 --> 00:12:35.701
zey zaynen, in Rusland iz dokh an ander lebn gevezn.

00:12:35.479 --> 00:12:38.030
, ir redt vegn di,

00:12:38.543 --> 00:12:40.815
di vos zaynen gekumen nokh der milkhome,

00:12:41.158 --> 00:12:43.458
neyn, velkhe zaynen gekumen

00:12:41.374 --> 00:12:42.374
yo?

00:12:43.458 --> 00:12:46.074
in tsayt; zey zaynen arayn

00:12:45.513 --> 00:12:47.409
oh, baym onheyb?

00:12:46.074 --> 00:12:49.306
in, in eyn un fertsikstn yor zaynen zey arayn.

00:12:49.306 --> 00:12:51.904
un dan hobn zey genumen shikn a sakh

00:12:51.904 --> 00:12:54.984
mentshn tsu lebn in Rige; zey hobn gevelt

00:12:54.984 --> 00:12:57.959
makhn az Ri- az Letland zol vern

00:12:56.142 --> 00:12:57.358
ah.

00:12:58.168 --> 00:13:00.283
tsugetey- tsuge-

00:13:00.828 --> 00:13:04.659
o, ven di, ven di rusn zaynen arayn. iz...

00:13:00.987 --> 00:13:03.321
tsugeteylt tsu Rusland, ya.

00:13:03.321 --> 00:13:06.624
nu, zaynen gekumen a sakh yidn lebn; yidn zukhn dokh

00:13:06.624 --> 00:13:07.967
vu s'iz beser.

00:13:07.735 --> 00:13:08.487
OKAY.

00:13:08.487 --> 00:13:15.726
iz, vos zaynen geven ayere batsiungen mit di poyerim? ven, ven hot ir, tsum bayshpil, zey gezen? baym mark ⟨ho-⟩...?

00:13:15.685 --> 00:13:19.256
neyn. umgefer, bay undz oyfn trep hot gelebt

00:13:19.465 --> 00:13:21.990
⟨SILIŅŠ⟩. er hot gehat a bud.

00:13:23.987 --> 00:13:25.499
er iz gevezn a let.

00:13:25.945 --> 00:13:29.273
⟨THEN⟩ iz gevezn ⟨G-⟩...

00:13:30.290 --> 00:13:33.026
, vi hot er geheysn?

00:13:38.820 --> 00:13:43.454
i- ikh gedenk nit, nor er flegt handlen mit, shn- v- mashinen,

00:13:43.579 --> 00:13:48.726
 nu, shveynem-, neymashinen.

00:13:50.789 --> 00:13:54.019
 vos vil ikh oysbrengen? ⟨VOT dize⟩ tsvey,

00:13:53.701 --> 00:13:55.884
uhuh., antshuldikt,

00:13:54.295 --> 00:13:55.504
zey hobn gelebt mer...

00:13:55.884 --> 00:13:58.473
 zey volt men gerufn "poyerim?"

00:13:57.754 --> 00:14:00.971
ya, di zaynen gevezn poyerim, rikhtike poyerim.

00:14:01.095 --> 00:14:02.422
nor vos vil...

00:14:01.146 --> 00:14:06.564
ober zey hobn gearbet nisht vi poyerim; zey hobn gearbet vi, geshefts-mentshn demolt.

00:14:04.302 --> 00:14:07.637
neyn, neyn. eyner hot gehat a bud untn.

00:14:07.744 --> 00:14:10.134
er flegt farkoyfn dortn farshidene,

00:14:10.275 --> 00:14:13.391
, esnvarg un

00:14:13.431 --> 00:14:15.735
kerosin dortn ⟨tsu⟩...

00:14:16.333 --> 00:14:22.908
un der flegt handlen, ⟨ah⟩, mit neymashinen. ir veyst vos a neymashin iz?

00:14:22.133 --> 00:14:23.466
yo, tsum shnaydn.

00:14:23.151 --> 00:14:25.473
 tsu, a mashin tsum neyen.

00:14:24.737 --> 00:14:27.498
o, tsum neyen? azoy vi sveters, un,

00:14:25.716 --> 00:14:27.127
tsum neyen.

00:14:27.302 --> 00:14:28.308
ya.

00:14:28.062 --> 00:14:29.220
 farrikhtn...?

00:14:29.192 --> 00:14:33.455
SH-, SHEW, SHEW...

00:14:34.187 --> 00:14:35.548
vi heyst es?

00:14:35.706 --> 00:14:37.067
a ⟨shveyney⟩mashin?

00:14:36.887 --> 00:14:37.944
a neymashin.

00:14:37.630 --> 00:14:39.294
a neymashin, ya?

00:14:38.011 --> 00:14:39.784
a ⟨SE-⟩ a SEWING MACHINE.

00:14:39.835 --> 00:14:41.921
 iz,

00:14:39.923 --> 00:14:40.514
yo.

00:14:41.921 --> 00:14:45.049
ot vil ikh aykh dertseyln di tsvey faktn:

00:14:45.173 --> 00:14:47.580
az di daytshn zaynen arayngekumen,

00:14:50.033 --> 00:14:53.925
bin ikh eyn mol farbaygegangen, shoyn, ikh bin shoyn gevezn in geto.

00:14:54.454 --> 00:14:58.671
bin ikh farbaygegangen dem S- bud ⟨SILIŅŠ'⟩.

00:14:59.635 --> 00:15:03.645
nor azoy vi undz hot gefirt a privater,

00:15:04.208 --> 00:15:08.639
bin ikh aroys fun di kleyn- nu, mir zaynen gevezn a man

00:15:08.639 --> 00:15:09.858
tsen efsher.

00:15:09.928 --> 00:15:12.925
bin ikh aroysgelofn un arayngelofn bay im in bud.

00:15:13.219 --> 00:15:16.503
ikh hob aykh dertseylt; ikh bin zeyer a RISKOVANNer gevezn.

00:15:16.527 --> 00:15:17.415
kh'hob nit...

00:15:16.528 --> 00:15:17.528
a vos?

00:15:17.691 --> 00:15:21.279
a RISKOVANN- ikh hob nit moyre gehat far keyn zakh.

00:15:21.640 --> 00:15:23.490
ikh bin arayngelofn bay im.

00:15:23.563 --> 00:15:25.126
er hot mir derzen,

00:15:26.010 --> 00:15:30.016
hot er mir gegebn a shtikl broyt, hot mir gegebn a shtikl puter.

00:15:30.016 --> 00:15:31.854
vos er hot mir gegebn UNK ayngepakt,

00:15:31.854 --> 00:15:34.290
un ikh bin aroys un ikh bin vider avek mit di,

00:15:35.393 --> 00:15:40.247
mit di kolone, nu, mit di mentshn vos ikh darf geyn.

00:15:40.742 --> 00:15:43.993
nu, ven es volt ge- bagleyt undz a daytsh,

00:15:44.202 --> 00:15:45.529
volt er es

00:15:45.585 --> 00:15:46.856
nit derlozn,

00:15:46.856 --> 00:15:49.325
ober ⟨az⟩ es bagleyt a privater mentsh,

00:15:50.038 --> 00:15:53.662
hot er farshtanen az ikh bin arayngelofn

00:15:53.972 --> 00:15:55.603
vos tsu krign, vo-...

00:15:56.318 --> 00:15:58.910
vayl di letn flegn undz helfn a sakh.

00:16:00.148 --> 00:16:01.694
un der tsveyter,

00:16:02.207 --> 00:16:04.597
hob ikh gehat mit im a geshprekh.

00:16:04.688 --> 00:16:06.116
dos iz shoyn nokh,

00:16:06.696 --> 00:16:10.470
gevezn di, di daytshn zaynen shoyn gevezn arayngekumen.

00:16:11.472 --> 00:16:15.727
hot er mit mir ge- hot er geredt mit mir, ⟨hot⟩...

00:16:16.163 --> 00:16:18.401
az zey zaynen shlekhte mentshn.

00:16:19.015 --> 00:16:21.658
er hot zeyer shlekht zikh opgerufn fun,

00:16:22.187 --> 00:16:25.353
fun di daytshn, zayendik a let,

00:16:25.444 --> 00:16:27.598
KHOTYA zayne tsvey zin

00:16:29.612 --> 00:16:32.642
zaynen avek in armey, in daytsh⟨ishe⟩.

00:16:33.021 --> 00:16:35.884
ober nokh di krig hob ikh zey nit gezen mer.

00:16:38.826 --> 00:16:41.688
nu, un dertseylt mir faktn, zogt er az

00:16:41.712 --> 00:16:44.062
di daytshn veln say vi say farshpiln.

00:16:44.062 --> 00:16:45.620
dos redt er mit mir:

00:16:45.964 --> 00:16:48.911
"zey hobn ongehoybn di krig, ober zey veln farshpiln,

00:16:48.934 --> 00:16:51.155
vayle zey hobn nit mit vemen tsu

00:16:52.103 --> 00:16:54.328
kemfn. zey hobn nit keyn..."

00:16:54.756 --> 00:16:56.589
"ITAL'YANTSY," zogt er,

00:16:57.861 --> 00:17:00.406
"zaynen nit keyn soldatn, vayle

00:17:00.406 --> 00:17:03.980
di EF- EFIOP- di EF- EFI-" nu,

00:17:04.290 --> 00:17:05.617
EFIOP⟨I-...⟩

00:17:05.488 --> 00:17:06.579
ETHIOPIA?

00:17:06.130 --> 00:17:07.052
ya.

00:17:07.210 --> 00:17:09.870
"hot zey tseklapt kimat."

00:17:10.281 --> 00:17:16.063
azoy arum, er flegt mit mir OTKRYTerhey-, UNK, fray reydn.

00:17:16.575 --> 00:17:18.695
er flegt nit moyre hobn far mir.

00:17:19.663 --> 00:17:23.184
nu, dos vil ikh oysbrengen, az s'zaynen gevezn farshidene.

00:17:23.291 --> 00:17:24.466
farshidene.

00:17:27.325 --> 00:17:30.913
kent ir bashraybn, vos hot pasirt,

00:17:31.628 --> 00:17:34.659
in ayer gegnt, onheybndik in nayn un draysik?

00:17:37.416 --> 00:17:42.793
mir hobn in nayn un draysikstn yor nor geleyent

00:17:43.120 --> 00:17:44.568
fun di tsaytungen

00:17:44.568 --> 00:17:46.286
vos es kumt for.

00:17:47.102 --> 00:17:50.116
nu, azoy vi yidn, hobn mir gekukt

00:17:50.545 --> 00:17:52.896
vos kumt for mit yidn dortn.

00:17:53.262 --> 00:17:55.376
az es iz oysgebrokhn a...

00:17:55.376 --> 00:17:58.270
in nayn un draysikstn hot dokh shoyn ongehoybn di krig.

00:17:58.270 --> 00:18:02.016
er iz dokh shoyn gegangen in, UNK, Tshekhoslovakye hot er tsugenumen,

00:18:02.016 --> 00:18:03.920
AVSTRIYA hot er tsugenumen.

00:18:04.062 --> 00:18:06.941
nu, un er iz shoyn, mir dakht zikh, arayn in Poyln.

00:18:07.065 --> 00:18:08.870
ikh gedenk nit genoy.

00:18:09.580 --> 00:18:11.936
hobn mir shoyn farshtanen az

00:18:12.128 --> 00:18:14.214
er vet zikh dokh nit opshteln.

00:18:14.592 --> 00:18:17.370
azoy arum az mentshn hobn shoyn getrakht,

00:18:17.578 --> 00:18:19.698
"vos heybt men on tsu ton?"

00:18:19.890 --> 00:18:20.879
ober

00:18:21.325 --> 00:18:24.474
zogn az mir hobn in nayn un draysikstn yor

00:18:25.155 --> 00:18:26.600
gefilt

00:18:27.332 --> 00:18:29.402
z- zeyer dem,

00:18:29.402 --> 00:18:34.244
dem, dem, de- di, di, dem d- druk fun...

00:18:34.791 --> 00:18:37.755
ken men nit zogn, vayle di rusn zaynen arayn in

00:18:35.530 --> 00:18:36.242
⟨⟩.

00:18:38.571 --> 00:18:40.117
fertsikstn yor.

00:18:40.815 --> 00:18:42.969
zey zaynen arayn in fertsikstn yor.

00:18:42.891 --> 00:18:44.687
un vos hot pasirt dan?

00:18:49.540 --> 00:18:52.284
ikh bin grade gevezn bayn tatn

00:18:52.678 --> 00:18:53.971
in verk-shtub,

00:18:54.433 --> 00:18:58.376
un vi zey ⟨z-⟩ zaynen gegangen fun MOS- fun DAUGAVPILS,

00:18:58.737 --> 00:19:00.958
fun yene zayt zaynen zey gekumen.

00:19:02.230 --> 00:19:04.974
nu, hob ikh gezen vi zey zaynen arayn, ⟨⟩,

00:19:05.166 --> 00:19:09.074
mit di pushkes, mit di soldatn, ⟨mit di⟩...

00:19:11.403 --> 00:19:13.783
 nu, un

00:19:13.823 --> 00:19:16.466
vos hot zikh ongehoybn? hot men ongehoybn

00:19:16.557 --> 00:19:20.262
shlogn di letishe politsay,

00:19:20.640 --> 00:19:22.282
di letishe ⟨a-⟩

00:19:22.716 --> 00:19:25.119
a sakh letishe mentshn.

00:19:27.829 --> 00:19:30.590
a sakh yidn hobn zikh arayngemisht

00:19:30.883 --> 00:19:32.041
in dem.

00:19:32.301 --> 00:19:36.342
zey zaynen gevorn,...

00:19:41.633 --> 00:19:43.399
nu, zey hobn ge-...

00:19:43.708 --> 00:19:46.503
gvardeytses, azoy hot men gerufn zey.

00:19:46.763 --> 00:19:48.616
gvardeytses, vi...

00:19:48.051 --> 00:19:49.051
vos heyst?

00:19:48.616 --> 00:19:49.912
a gvardye.

00:19:50.560 --> 00:19:53.290
vos yidn zaynen gevorn gvardeytses?

00:19:52.146 --> 00:19:54.047
ya, zey flegn helfn,

00:19:54.441 --> 00:19:55.970
zey flegn...

00:19:57.917 --> 00:20:02.222
ir vey- ⟨s'iz a sakh⟩, tsvishn yidn zaynen dokh farshidene do mentshn,

00:20:02.222 --> 00:20:04.428
ober di yungere ⟨v-⟩

00:20:04.428 --> 00:20:05.572
flegn

00:20:06.608 --> 00:20:07.867
helfn...

00:20:08.262 --> 00:20:10.298
zey hobn gemeynt az di rusn,

00:20:10.894 --> 00:20:13.048
vet zayn beser vi di letn.

00:20:14.252 --> 00:20:18.128
nor s'zaynen, es iz gevezn nit keyn sakh f- tsvishn zey.

00:20:19.888 --> 00:20:24.187
vos hot ir gezen? vi azoy hot di lage zikh gebitn in ayer gegnt?

00:20:24.512 --> 00:20:27.645
ir hot gekent mentshn vos hobn onteyl genumen

00:20:24.748 --> 00:20:25.974
 bay...

00:20:28.225 --> 00:20:29.691
in di,

00:20:29.946 --> 00:20:31.712
in di gesheenishn dan?

00:20:34.266 --> 00:20:37.550
keyn groyse gesheenishn iz nit gevezn, vayle,

00:20:39.430 --> 00:20:41.719
di armey iz gevezn a shtarke,

00:20:41.843 --> 00:20:43.102
di rusishe.

00:20:43.648 --> 00:20:46.426
nor vos, me hot likvidirt

00:20:46.467 --> 00:20:49.127
di, s'iz gevezn di

00:20:49.622 --> 00:20:51.860
politsey profektur...

00:20:52.002 --> 00:20:53.650
⟨s'heyst⟩ a profektur?

00:20:54.178 --> 00:20:55.218
vos iz dos?

00:20:55.056 --> 00:20:58.020
dos iz di ho- nu, azoy vi der

00:20:58.077 --> 00:20:59.280
QUARTER

00:20:59.280 --> 00:21:00.382
in...

00:21:00.387 --> 00:21:03.082
⟨p-⟩ p- polits- politseyske...

00:21:01.238 --> 00:21:03.419
, POLICE STATION?

00:21:03.443 --> 00:21:05.614
ya, a STATION, ya.

00:21:03.845 --> 00:21:04.521
uhuh.

00:21:05.856 --> 00:21:09.191
dos hot men likvidirt, di ale politseyske,

00:21:10.243 --> 00:21:12.177
vu zey zaynen gevezn.

00:21:13.213 --> 00:21:15.519
un me hot genum-...

00:21:13.888 --> 00:21:17.167
dos hot ir gezen tsi gehert vegn dem?

00:21:16.386 --> 00:21:18.439
dos hob ikh,

00:21:19.930 --> 00:21:21.679
gezen vayle

00:21:22.005 --> 00:21:24.394
ikh fleg arumloyfn iber di gasn.

00:21:24.874 --> 00:21:26.671
kh'fleg arumloyfn iber di gasn.

00:21:25.048 --> 00:21:26.992
vos hot ir gezen?

00:21:26.671 --> 00:21:30.372
keyn shiseray iz nit gevezn, keyn shlogeray iz nit gevezn.

00:21:30.578 --> 00:21:32.321
nor ikh bin a...

00:21:30.781 --> 00:21:34.131
ir't gezen vi m'hot ge- av- avekgefirt mentshn?

00:21:34.138 --> 00:21:35.763
di rusn hobn,

00:21:35.763 --> 00:21:38.722
hob ikh nit gezen az zey hobn avekgefirt mentshn,

00:21:41.569 --> 00:21:43.650
 nor zey,

00:21:44.432 --> 00:21:46.771
zey hobn gemakht take an ander,

00:21:47.098 --> 00:21:49.474
zey hobn gevelt an ander firung makhn.

00:21:53.072 --> 00:21:56.861
s'zaynen gevezn soldatn, tog un nakht flegn zey zayn oyf di gasn.

00:21:56.861 --> 00:21:58.095
lebn undzer gas

00:21:58.405 --> 00:21:59.777
iz gevezn,

00:21:59.777 --> 00:22:01.335
geshtanen, ikh veys nit,

00:22:02.893 --> 00:22:04.729
a man tsvantsik.

00:22:04.729 --> 00:22:07.629
oyf yeder gas flegn ⟨sh- zay-⟩ zaynen gevezn di soldatn,

00:22:08.226 --> 00:22:11.459
biz vanet s'hot zikh ayngeshtilt a bisinke.

00:22:12.158 --> 00:22:13.698
ir farshteyt dokh,

00:22:13.698 --> 00:22:16.505
di letn hobn nit holt di rusn gehat.

00:22:16.883 --> 00:22:19.259
letn hobn gelebt aleyn;

00:22:19.259 --> 00:22:21.230
zey hobn gehat zeyer land

00:22:21.574 --> 00:22:23.812
un zey hobn gelebt vi zey hobn gevelt,

00:22:24.055 --> 00:22:25.517
un do...

00:22:26.653 --> 00:22:29.313
der opmakh mit GITLERn,

00:22:29.488 --> 00:22:31.372
rusn mit GITLERn,

00:22:32.273 --> 00:22:35.709
iz oysgekumen az zey, az zey zaynen arayn in Letland,

00:22:36.289 --> 00:22:38.291
un GITLER iz arayn in Poyln.

00:22:39.662 --> 00:22:41.480
 iz,

00:22:41.875 --> 00:22:43.961
iz di lage gevorn

00:22:44.052 --> 00:22:45.919
beser, erger

00:22:46.363 --> 00:22:48.466
far di yidn, volt ir gezogt?

00:22:48.321 --> 00:22:52.719
⟨nu, f- di,⟩ u- mir yidn hobn es nit gefilt.

00:22:53.063 --> 00:22:56.212
keyner hot undz nit geshlogn, keyner hot undz nit...

00:22:56.623 --> 00:23:01.629
vayle in di rusishe armey un di rusn dortn zaynen dokh oykh a sakh yidn gevezn.

00:23:01.770 --> 00:23:03.844
zey hobn nisht gevolt,

00:23:03.961 --> 00:23:08.207
 aveknemen di firmes, tsum bayshpil, fun di balebatim?

00:23:06.546 --> 00:23:09.814
dos hobn zey alts NATSIONALIZIRt;

00:23:10.208 --> 00:23:13.959
zey hobn tsugenumen di hayzer, zey hobn tsugenumen fabrikn.

00:23:13.959 --> 00:23:15.064
dos heyst

00:23:15.064 --> 00:23:17.509
NATSIONALIZATS⟨I⟩.

00:23:17.717 --> 00:23:19.854
dos hobn zey altsding tsugenumen.

00:23:21.233 --> 00:23:26.363
iz, bay aykh hot men genumen ayer tate's gesheft?

